Package: GLCMTextures
Title: Calculates GLCM Textures of raster layers
Version: 0.3.5
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Alexander",
           family = "Ilich",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "ailich@usf.edu",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-1758-8499"))
Description: Calculates GLCM textures of raster layers using a sliding rectangular window. Also includes functions to quantize a raster into grey levels as well as tabulate a glcm and calculate glcm texture metrics for a matrix.
